atar":"","nickname":"","note":"","ucode":"","race_medal":0,"user_type":1,"is_pvip":false},"discussion":{"id":371370,"discussion_content":"对。在“历史思维”上，中小互联网企业往往是机会主义和生存驱动的不是趋势驱动的；在“生态思维”上，中小企业很少有联盟、协同意识，更多是完整搭建；在“系统搭建”上，中小企业混乱无序。","likes_number":0,"is_delete":false,"is_hidden":false,"ctime":1619748700,"is_liked":false,"can_delete":false,"is_complain":false,"is_top":false,"parent_id":0,"ip_address":""},"score":2,"extra":"","child_discussion_number":0,"child_discussions":[]},{"author":{"id":1031388,"avatar":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/0f/bc/dc/108ad1eb.jpg","nickname":"钰湚—付晓岩","note":"","ucode":"75AE9EE36103FD","race_medal":0,"user_type":2,"is_pvip":true},"reply_author":{"id":0,"avatar":"","nickname":"","note":"","ucode":"","race_medal":0,"user_type":1,"is_pvip":false},"discussion":{"id":368550,"discussion_content":"感谢您的指正，其实立意上不是说互联网一定强，而是大家都认可数字化转型成功的企业科技属性应该是比较强的，而不是传统上由纯业务人员占绝大多数这种企业形态，目前互联网只是比较接近这种形态，我倒是认为以后的数字化企业范本很可能来自转型成功的工业企业。至于做的一塌糊涂的互联网中小企业，这个问题属于经营问题，而不是组织形态问题，经营差的传统企业也很多，毕竟，从企业数量上来看，传统企业更多。","likes_number":0,"is_delete":false,"is_hidden":false,"ctime":1618749685,"is_liked":false,"can_delete":false,"is_complain":false,"is_top":false,"parent_id":0,"ip_address":""},"score":2,"extra":"","child_discussion_number":0,"child_discussions":[]}]},{"had_liked":false,"id":289284,"user_name":"陈从宾","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1208178,"ip_address":"","ucode":"4005828A0A6E3C","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/12/6f/72/21b31a2f.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1618968797,"is_pvip":false,"replies":[{"id":"104994","content":"是的，做一个深度思考者","user_name":"作者回复","comment_id":289284,"uid":"1031388","ip_address":"","utype":1,"ctime":1619001914,"user_name_real":"钰湚—付晓岩"}],"discussion_count":2,"race_medal":0,"score":"27388772573","product_id":100076501,"comment_content":"对个人发展而言：解决问题的方法论，要比问题的答案更重要。答案太多记不住，记住找到答案的方法，反而更简单，信息越少记忆越好。","like_count":6,"discussions":[{"author":{"id":1031388,"avatar":"https://stat